  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Ilosian Jade is a beautiful translucent green stone.<o:=
p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>It is mined in great slabs from riverbed rocks. Ilosian
  jade is found exclusively on Marshy Swamp worlds.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Occurrence: very rare<o:p></o:p></span></p>
